comments: Fox (SAC) legally dislodges the ball from Bridges (CHA) during his drive.
Davis (SAC) cleanly blocks Hayward's (CHA) shot near the rim.
Bridges (CHA) begins to lose control of the ball before the incidental contact to the hand by Davis (SAC).
Hayward (CHA) does not step out of bounds upon retrieving the loose ball.
Thor (CHA) makes contact with Fox's (SAC) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Martin (CHA) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Hayward (CHA) avoids delivering any contact to Fox (SAC).

Replay review of the foul called on Davis (SAC) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Davis (SAC) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Martin (CHA), but Martin's foot returns to the floor before completing his shooting motion and the basket is not counted.  Martin receives two free throws.
Martin (CHA) commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).
Bagley III (SAC) attempts the putback and the contact by Hayward (CHA) and Bridges (CHA) is incidental.
Oubre Jr. (CHA) makes marginal contact with Fox (SC) during the rebounding sequence.
Hayward (CHA) legally defends the play at the basket by Davis (SAC) and the contact is incidental.
